287
00:14:17,265 --> 00:14:20,723
About you and Pearson?

288
00:14:20,768 --> 00:14:24,329
What makes
you think so?

289
00:14:24,372 --> 00:14:26,636
I didn't understand
the situation.

290
00:14:28,876 --> 00:14:30,173
What situation?

291
00:14:30,278 --> 00:14:33,008
The situation you're probably
writing the book about.

292
00:14:33,047 --> 00:14:34,742
Probably what situation?

293
00:14:34,782 --> 00:14:36,773
The way I feel
about it is this:

294
00:14:36,818 --> 00:14:39,810
I believe that Pearson's
