299
00:14:50,531 --> 00:14:52,431
He told me on the airplane.

300
00:14:52,467 --> 00:14:54,025
Who told you what?

301
00:14:54,068 --> 00:14:55,035
Goose told me.

302
00:14:55,069 --> 00:14:56,058
Why?

303
00:14:57,939 --> 00:15:00,032
I've been calling Pearson

304
00:15:00,074 --> 00:15:03,441
"Romeo and Juliet:
Which is which," see?

305
00:15:03,478 --> 00:15:06,106
Now who'll you tell?

306
00:15:06,147 --> 00:15:08,012
Nobody, Arthur!

307
00:15:08,049 --> 00:15:10,244
Absolutely nobody!

308
00:15:13,421 --> 00:15:15,389
I told the wife,
and that's the end of it.

309
00:15:15,423 --> 00:15:18,915
Why "told the wife"?

310
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:23,897
Arthur,
I tell the wife everything.

311
00:15:27,201 --> 00:15:29,328
Hello, Doc.

312
00:15:29,370 --> 00:15:30,837
Sidney.

313
00:15:30,872 --> 00:15:31,839
What's up?

314
00:15:31,873 --> 00:15:32,999
Where is everybody?

315
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:34,371
Nobody knows.

316
00:15:38,212 --> 00:15:39,509
I'll bet Tootsie knows.

317
00:15:39,547 --> 00:15:40,571
Knows what, Arthur?

318
00:15:40,615 --> 00:15:42,310
Now look,
I know something is up.

319
00:15:42,350 --> 00:15:44,716
The long distance
been flying far and fast.

320
00:15:46,053 --> 00:15:49,318
I could use two grandstands
any weekend or night.

321
00:15:49,357 --> 00:15:52,349
Yeah, well, tickets are going
to be scarcer and scarcer

322
00:15:52,393 --> 00:15:53,360
from here on in.

323
00:15:53,394 --> 00:15:55,191
Why did I see Doc Loftus

324
00:15:55,229 --> 00:15:56,696
just pass through?

325
00:15:56,731 --> 00:15:59,199
Oh, Doc Loftus in the hotel?

326
00:15:59,233 --> 00:16:03,101
Doc Loftus, telephone, please.

327
00:16:03,137 --> 00:16:04,536
Who wants him?

328
00:16:04,572 --> 00:16:06,039
Dutch wants him.

329
00:16:06,073 --> 00:16:07,370
Who's sick?

330
00:16:07,408 --> 00:16:09,205
I don't know,
somebody in Minnesota.

