343
00:16:39,907 --> 00:16:42,603
You are in the doghouse.

344
00:16:42,643 --> 00:16:43,769
Why you?

345
00:16:43,811 --> 00:16:45,836
You've been playing
your heart out.

346
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:48,906
It's some of those other
so-called baseball players

347
00:16:48,950 --> 00:16:50,440
been dragging their foot.

348
00:16:50,484 --> 00:16:52,418
That's why
