349
00:16:52,453 --> 00:16:54,421
Why me?

350
00:16:54,455 --> 00:16:56,355
Because of your contract,
Pearson...

351
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:58,358
Mr. Rogers

352
00:16:58,392 --> 00:17:01,384
the detective, broke it open.

353
00:17:01,429 --> 00:17:02,691
You see, very easy.

354
00:17:02,730 --> 00:17:04,630
Joe Jaros and Goose Williams

355
00:17:04,665 --> 00:17:07,566
spent the winter in Minnesota
with Pearson.

356
00:17:07,602 --> 00:17:11,163
You know, I didn't even know
