357
00:17:11,205 --> 00:17:12,729
Well, takes all kinds.

358
00:17:15,376 --> 00:17:17,037
The time is 8:06.

359
00:17:17,078 --> 00:17:21,572
Third base side, Arthur,
lower deck, not too far back

